{"tid":2003439,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[去到凌晨個熱門就群魔亂舞] 開多次講下開遮、和理非","createTime":"2020-05-05T21:20:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-08T07:16:55.000Z","uid":54564,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6d546029ff6a5edb8ac5b92c28e7e380c6bf003b","tid":2003439,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T21:20:00.000Z","msg":"夜麻麻一撳入去熱門會嚇親，好多都係創意台同娛樂台<br />\n(明白大家都需要放鬆下, 但比例多到係佔咗一半咁濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n開宗明義講番10/05 有九龍大遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/fJALnjd.jpg\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/ozEDHkm.jpg\" /></blockquote><br />\n而去遊行，就需要補充下出去嘅mind set，唔好淨係鳩企<br />\n<br />\n 「落雨，開遮」 比你想像中更有用 <br />\n如果tldr可以拉到最底<br />\n<br />\n遮 喺香港抗爭當中有好多作用 <br />\n<br />\n一 可以擋子彈<br />\n二 可以用作自衛 (總比手無寸鐵好）<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">三 就係可以用嚟cover手足</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n咁多個月以嚟大家都知道見到狗錄你影嘅時候要開遮<br />\n當手足做嘢 (無論換衫 裝修 私鳥）嘅時候要開遮<br />\n<em><ins>但係普遍人淨係記得&quot;行動中&quot;開遮<br />\n忽略咗&quot;離場&quot;都要開遮</ins></em><br />\n<br />\n好簡單舉例子(以下圖片都係google是但揾)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2P6Nk05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2P6Nk05.jpg&h=a3bdc0f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sm9jb7N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsm9jb7N.jpg&h=12c1f3c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你會見到<strong>手足嘅身高 服飾 髮型 裝備 打扮特徵全部都已經被影低晒 </strong><br />\n咁班狗就可以透過cctv揾番呢一身打扮嘅人 <br />\n<strong>由邊度出現 活動完咗之後去邊 搭咩車走等等</strong><br />\n<br />\n所以點解好多人打完狗/ 裝修完/ 魔法完 過咗2-3個月 就會比狗上門咬 <br />\n<em><ins>因為佢哋可以睇幾百上千個鐘片</ins></em> 為咗咬你呢位「極端核心激進勇武分子」<br />\n<br />\n但係如果手足行動嗰陣 有真係落雨開遮<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uLpZWBo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuLpZWBo.jpg&h=00794153&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好似平時旁聽師咁cover手足<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>然後手足行動完嘅時候有人群遮陣掩護佢走<br />\n</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/60ndgBq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F60ndgBq.jpg&h=8318a9df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好似咁樣 講真你唔會揾得番到底係邊個人落手<br />\n<br />\n所以想呼籲大家 <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">無論乜人都好 出街一定要帶把遮</span></strong><br />\n無論長遮又好 縮骨遮都好<br />\n當有手足做嘢 唔好成碌木咁企喺度/打卡拍片<br />\n你同身邊嘅人一齊開遮行過去 <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">掩護手足行動 <br />\n掩護手足退場</span></strong><br />\n務求令手足盡量唔好落入cctv/ 鏡頭之下<br />\n<br />\n唔好再好似以前咁淨係鳩叫完開遮<br />\n又遮唔到手足 行動完又唔掩護手足離場<br />\n咁樣開遮係無能用的<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我心目中理想嘅狀況</span></ins><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">1. 人要夠多 (最好full blackbloc)</span></strong><br />\n2. 手足行動嘅時候幫手開遮cover<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">3. 手足行動完 遮陣照包圍到手足 然後手足融入番遊行大部隊/ 一齊開遮融入遮陣之後離開</span><br />\n<em><ins>(我個人覺得離場最重要 就算入場/郁手嗰陣入咗鏡 但唔知手足之後走去邊的話 理論上都好難揾得番手足）</ins></em><br />\n4. 然後收遮 咁手足嘅特徵最可能被保護得到 班狗都好難追番cctv<br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家討論下點做會更好<br />\n但我覺得遮陣保護手足係必須"},{"pid":"1d30576ffdef13bc381a03980ad2dfedb40aab6d","tid":2003439,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T21:20:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>除咗開遮、帶物資, 出到去仲有好多嘢做<br />\n見到有唔小巴打喺之前個post都有留言 順勢quote埋過嚟<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>推,麻煩仲要報埋哨<br />\n好多盲頭烏蠅唔睇哨gp前面有水炮車都仲衝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可以幫手報哨 / 睇哨channel做現場消息傳播員<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>同時請大家black bloc得好啲</blockquote><br />\nblack bloc要包實d自己 + 離場要留意提防跟尾狗<br />\n<br />\n記住真係要be water <br />\n唔好掛住撚狗/ 死守/ 陣地<br />\n個人建議做每樣嘢都要一擊即中, 達到目的就要收手<br />\n唔好比機會班狗圍死 人無事下次先可以繼續出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"4cb84b128ea233e35e53ba5bcda9765e2546e9f7","tid":2003439,"uid":54564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T21:21:53.000Z","msg":"除此之外我本身都想推動番各個和理非繼續保持下熱誠參與抗爭<br />\n唔敢勇武 和理非唔知做乜好？入嚟睇下啦！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2002356\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2002356</a><br />\n<blockquote>發覺近日有唔小朋友都同我講 佢都好想繼續參與抗爭 但係唔知可以做咩好 <br />\n<br />\n聽完我都好開心佢起碼會想揾d嘢做下等自己團火唔好熄滅<br />\n<br />\n其實<strong><ins>和理非除咗課金 食黃店之外仲有好多嘢可以做</ins></strong><br />\n沿用番上年10 11月嘅文宣為例<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AxvCXPv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAxvCXPv.jpg&h=5f8c4991&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RziXXPx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRziXXPx.jpg&h=c3d2c65d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pFnxMHT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpFnxMHT.jpg&h=f8599578&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以做嘅嘢有好多<br />\n聯署師 貼紙師 上庭師 文宣師 網上戰線師 大把嘢係大家可以日常一齊做<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔好諗住自己唔敢勇武就咩都唔做</span></span><br />\n每次見手足被捕 被控告 淨係好嬲好嬲係無用的<br />\n<br />\n同埋小弟都想喺度<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>拜托下文宣手足再出番呢啲可以比人spread 一齊challenge 嘅文宣</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n近期見好多文宣都好資訊性 好靚 會講時事 但忽略咗推動和理非一齊同行<br />\n我哋要識be water 唔係一招用完唔work就唔用<br />\n<br />\n而係用完 喺合適時候都可以攞番出嚟再用過！<br />\n<br />\n同場為5月10號遊行加映<br />\n仲有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一個星期唔夠就出發</span> 點解都無乜人推遊行post??<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FAK4CRo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFAK4CRo.jpg&h=757e0c95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fJALnjd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfJALnjd.jpg&h=832566c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n手足們應承我 番去6 7月咁 <br />\n大家一推番行動post 有用post 好無？</span></span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"99de54a942b432f8a74be207725d68974507316a","tid":2003439,"uid":54564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T21:23:49.000Z","msg":"同埋喺隔離post見到 全民做哨真係好重要<br />\n<br />\n齊做哨兵，監視黑狗<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2002950\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2002950</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dY2ByQQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdY2ByQQ.jpg&h=ce1f89f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4sAzkvQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4sAzkvQ.jpg&h=64832855&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"203f83f6ca5d369d5620e1f7d436a1c611488260","tid":2003439,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T21:38:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"852337f51af79de4bfeee04fd79891d2776a641d","tid":2003439,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T21:40:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0874a5a1818454ef16475f07bf7662ee5649582b","tid":2003439,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T21:41:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"261f4d922d17c575d3041869caaab40d2e5d0739","tid":2003439,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T21:42:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60b92b7b379e359800d7564f77c963dd4d3a315d","tid":2003439,"uid":158888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T21:43:37.000Z","msg":"推有用post"},{"pid":"1ab47b35c4a4970dc8d085b8058c44cd10846bcf","tid":2003439,"uid":230511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T21:48:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ef74b4259019323438576fa0d1f8bcef5cd431f5","tid":2003439,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T22:00:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48da1c9011c52974dc5a0a28cc755415402b4d7f","tid":2003439,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T22:11:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7652380d1e4be917dd2d865d629b37058c02775","tid":2003439,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T23:13:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"55e7b6aef04d0c0349c8ea9cefb3502dc8a0b210","tid":2003439,"uid":95519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T23:17:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6d411755d57da6f58829212db5022e7ba35efb4f","tid":2003439,"uid":315534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T23:17:56.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80da5b609632eeec4d502bd6ad43475767e2cda7","tid":2003439,"uid":260814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T23:30:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4f48a5351fdbaf7020366fb6df004b56486feb90","tid":2003439,"uid":148017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T02:12:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">終極TLDR:除咗要跑就老閪都開返把遮</span></span>"},{"pid":"def8ebdd92674e50cebc89bafd445a5f106cb07f","tid":2003439,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T04:26:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18dc306039e3f9bc6409c64df70ce8c2332941ba","tid":2003439,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T04:27:04.000Z","msg":"開遮開遮開遮"},{"pid":"a3de22f516e09dee50d466889ce0516cf5b4f57e","tid":2003439,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T04:36:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5143a777034f6cd01b71aebadd2b8fb181b045cd","tid":2003439,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T05:00:55.000Z","msg":"開遮啊"},{"pid":"ce6bae6200097b6a1105cdac389a52ea583f578d","tid":2003439,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T05:03:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d12964fe5de3f6bd3d03b07b86fb5551cb78b88b","tid":2003439,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T05:15:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c674bf35a28fe49fa68187e292cbc9e4fb3ff81","tid":2003439,"uid":145574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T05:19:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"642872602b98146d323aad9c6851a0d618adcf24","tid":2003439,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T05:58:49.000Z","msg":"推到攰"}],"pinned":{"pid":"482fde743359c3998f0d2bc95c8cf44b6cf8dcc9","tid":2003439,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T07:16:55.000Z","msg":"今晚大家知咩事<br />\n<br />\n記得帶遮 開遮 好好善用把遮"}}